					<h1 class="mb-3">About VanWatch</h1>
					<p>VanWatch is a mobile application designed to enhance personal safety and security for individuals residing in or traveling to high-risk areas. Our primary objective is to provide users with real-time information and tools to help them navigate and stay safe in potentially dangerous situations.</p>
					<p>By leveraging advanced technology and community-driven data, VanWatch aims to empower users and enable them to make informed decisions about their safety.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center mt-4">
					<h2 class="mb-3">Functionality Description</h2>
					<p><strong>Real-time Crime Alerts:</strong> VanWatch utilizes a sophisticated network of sensors, data feeds, and user reports to detect and disseminate real-time crime information. Users receive immediate alerts about nearby criminal activities, allowing them to avoid potentially dangerous areas or take appropriate precautions.</p>
					<p><strong>High-risk Crime Area Indicators:</strong> The application provides visual indicators on a map, highlighting areas known for high crime rates or recent criminal incidents. This feature helps users plan their routes and make informed decisions about where to go, enabling them to avoid dangerous locations or exercise extra caution when necessary.</p>
					<p><strong>Personal Protective Tools:</strong> VanWatch offers a range of personal safety tools, such as a panic button, emergency contact integration, and virtual escort services. The panic button can be activated in distress situations, instantly alerting designated contacts or emergency services. The virtual escort feature allows users to share their location with trusted contacts, who can monitor their journey remotely and provide assistance if needed.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center mt-4">
					<h2 class="mb-3">Data and AI</h2>
					<p>At VanWatch, we collect crime-related data from reliable sources to provide users with a comprehensive history of crimes. We aim for continual crime record updates through user reports, ensuring constant crime monitoring. User privacy is our top priority. We do not collect personally identifiable information, and all user reports are processed anonymously, ensuring complete protection of personal information.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="text-center mt-4">
					<h2 class="mb-3">Our Team</h2>
					<p>The VanWatch team is comprised of four dedicated members: Jeen, Yunsang, Heeho, and Ning. Each team member brings unique expertise and skills to their respective roles. We work tirelessly to develop and improve VanWatch, with a shared vision to expand its reach beyond Vancouver, gather crime data worldwide, and build a user-centric application that prioritizes safety and security.</p>
